{"address1": "Bellona Building", "address2": "7th, 8th, 9th Floor, The Walk, Hiranandani Estate Ghodbunder Road, Thane West", "city": "Thane", "zip": "400 607", "country": "India", "phone": "91 22 6174 0100", "fax": "91 22 2173 5599", "website": "https://www.huhtamaki.com/en-in/flexible-packaging/", "industry": "Packaging & Containers", "industryKey": "packaging-containers", "industryDisp": "Packaging & Containers", "sector": "Consumer Cyclical", "sectorKey": "consumer-cyclical", "sectorDisp": "Consumer Cyclical", "longBusinessSummary": "Huhtamaki India Limited manufactures and sells of flexible consumer packaging and labelling solutions in India. It provides flexible packaging materials, pouches, and label for food and beverages, coffee, petfood, barrier protection, retort applications, healthcare, and industrial markets. The company also offers labels, including anti-counterfeit solutions, such as transfer, tamper-proof seal, backside printing and numbering, variable data, and hologram labels; functional labels comprising hanger, reclosable, braille, high and low-temperature resistant labels, and squeezable wrinkle-free labels for tubes and pouches; dome, metallic gold and silver printed, digital printed, tactile labels, and ultra-clear films; two and three-layer, and booklet labels; and shrink sleeves, and low migration and in-mould labels. In addition, it involves in laser engraving; supply of engraved cylinders; and offers mono-material products under the blueloop brand name. The company was formerly known as Huhtamaki PPL Limited and changed its name to Huhtamaki India Limited in November 2020. Huhtamaki India Limited was founded in 1935 and is based in Thane, India. Huhtamaki India Limited operates as a subsidiary of Huhtavefa BV.", "fullTimeEmployees": 2500, "companyOfficers": [{"maxAge": 1, "name": "Mr. Abhijaat Akhilesh Sinha", "title": "Company Secretary, Compliance Officer & Legal Counsel", "exercisedValue": 0, "unexercisedValue": 0}, {"maxAge": 1, "name